sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant Security as WebSecurityConfig
  participant Jwt as JwtAuthConverter
  participant Auth as AuthorisationService
  participant Controller as TenantController
  participant Resolver as TenantResolverService
  Client->>Security: Request with Bearer JWT
  Security->>Jwt: Convert JWT to Authentication
  Jwt->>Auth: Extract realm roles
  Auth-->>Jwt: Local AUTHORIZATION_* authorities
  Security->>Controller: Invoke protected endpoint
  Controller->>Auth: @PreAuthorize / tenant checks
  Controller->>Resolver: Resolve tenant context when needed
  Resolver-->>Controller: token, cookie, or subdomain tenant id
